ki","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Seabob","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Ringo","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Big Mable (sofa)","quantity":"1"},{"label":"SUP","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Kayak"},{"label":"Efoil"}],"entertainment":["Salon TV","Satellite TV","Onboard WIFI","Salon Stereo"],"tenders":["2 Tenders 15 + 80 Hp"]},"crew":[{"name":"Umit Kucuk","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cca2f1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fad1dcb0-ad93-11ef-8dd6-83c7c4cd6f15/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Captain Umit is 36 years old  and grew up in Fethiye. He started working in yacht Industry since he was 16. He's been the only captain of Long Island because of very satisfacting charters since he has been hired. He speaks turkish and english."},{"name":"Buket Gulham","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cca2f1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::083e2430-ad94-11ef-8dd6-83c7c4cd6f15/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Buket is 32 years old and she's born in Manisa. Now she lives in Fethiye. She is in yachting industry since 4 years. She takes care of layout and cleaning rooms."},{"name":"Melih Abdurrahmanoglu","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cca2f1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::27f18740-ad94-11ef-b183-97af828515a6/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Melih worked as chef in restaurants for 6 years since he joined the yachting indistry last year. He lives in Mugla. Specialized in meat and desserts. He divides the kitchen with Yagiz."},{"name":"Yagiz Coskun","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cca2f1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3832c0b0-ad94-11ef-b183-97af828515a6/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Yagiz is 24 years old and work in Long island kitchen with Melih. He graduated in Bodrum Culinary High School, in Mugla University Department of Food and beverages. He works in yachting industry since 3 years and he is specialized in seafood."},{"name":"Ilker Aydin","avatar":"/m